source.name: Public Health Statistics - Low birth weight in Chicago, by year, 1999 – 2009
source.description: This dataset contains the annual number of low birth weight births and the percent of total births these low birth weight births represent, with corresponding 95% confidence intervals, by Chicago community area, for the years 1999 – 2009. See full description at http://bit.ly/KcNNzH
